text: Patrika Darbo (born April 6, 1948 in Jacksonville, Florida) is an American movie and television actress. She played Nancy Wesley in the television soap opera Days of Our Lives. She also acted in independent movies. ==Awards and nominations== Year Award Work Result Ref 1999 Soap Opera Digest Award for Outstanding Female Newcomer Days of Our Lives 2000 Daytime Emmy Award for Outstanding Supporting Actress in a Drama Series 2016 Primetime Emmy Award for Best Actress in a Short Form Comedy or Drama Series Acting Dead ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Jacksonville, Florida Category:American television actors Category:Emmy Award winning actors
